[Joel]
Strings are shot.

773
00:49:31.885 --> 00:49:33.386
- Well... - I'll put some
new ones on for ya.

774
00:49:33.387 --> 00:49:34.720
Oh. you don't have
to do that. I...

775
00:49:34.721 --> 00:49:36.306
I can get it back tomorrow.

776
00:49:40.185 --> 00:49:41.186
